 "remarks": "Beautifully updated and maintained 4-bedroom home on a very desirable private cul-de-sac in South Wilton. This home offers a flexible layout, room for everyone, and a level manicured yard with an inground pool for relaxing or outdoor fun. The renovated eat-in kitchen is both stylish and functional, while the great room features vaulted ceilings, hard wood floors and is filled with natural light. Upstairs, the primary suite includes an updated bathroom with vaulted ceiling along with two additional bedrooms and another updated full bathroom. The lower level offers a spacious family room with a fireplace, built-ins and sliding doors that open to the expansive flat backyard, as well as a fourth bedroom and laundry room. Recent updates include new roof, well pump, driveway repaved, reverse osmosis system, and a/c. Located in a sought-after South Wilton neighborhood, this home offers easy access to both town center, highway and commuting train.",
